Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition
On July 26, 2017, HomeTrust Bancshares, Inc., the holding company for HomeTrust
Bank, issued a press release reporting 2017 financial results.  A copy of the
press release, including unaudited financial information released as a part
thereof, is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K and
incorporated by reference herein.
Item 9.01 Financial Statements and Exhibits
(d)      Exhibits
99.1 Press release dated July 26, 2017
